{"tid":227593,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【搵一套漫畫】幫幫手 童年回憶 想睇返","createTime":"2017-05-03T09:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T07:14:39.000Z","uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93d6b5086c888b621849a1ae9990342a88eb2750","tid":227593,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"套野應該18禁 少女漫畫黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨係記得有幕係男主角入左學校女更衣室 跟住唔知點解入左去某一格同女主角一齊淋花灑(好似係因為有人入更衣室 女主角為左掩護佢 等佢唔好俾人發現 就拉左佢入去淋花灑個位到)<br />\n<br />\n本漫畫我一定係2008年之前睇既 有全裸畫面但冇lin頭的 同埋好似有幕係雪地上面有個裸女出現 (我唔知係咪同其他漫畫撈亂左劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太耐記憶好模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有冇漫畫神人知本漫畫係乜名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc71116bb9a07cd8688d51769d48668c3873d2d","tid":227593,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"非h漫黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7919b126593788b78d5aa07821a1d643af1f479a","tid":227593,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"有冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}